1. *Ljubomorna* sam na tvoj uspeh. (I am *jealous* of your success.)
2. Ona je uvek *ljubomorna* na svoju sestru. (She is always *jealous* of her sister.)
3. Da li si *ljubomoran* na svog najboljeg prijatelja? (Are you *jealous* of your best friend?)
4. Ona nije želela da prizna da je *ljubomorna* na njegov uspeh. (She didn't want to admit that she was *jealous* of his success.)
5. Njen *ljubomoran* dečko stalno joj zamera što priča sa drugim muškarcima. (Her *jealous* boyfriend constantly accuses her of talking to other men.)
6. *Ljubomorne* oči komšinice pratile su svaki pokret nove devojke u zgradi. (The *jealous* eyes of the neighbor followed every move of the new girl in the building.)
7. Ona je bila *ljubomorna* na svoju prijateljicu zbog njenog novog dečka. (She was *jealous* of her friend because of her new boyfriend.)
8. Njegova *ljubomora* je uništila njihovu vezu. (His *jealousy* destroyed their relationship.)
9. Nikada nisam video tako *ljubomornog* muškarca. (I have never seen such a *jealous* man.)
10. Ona je pokušavala da prikrije svoju *ljubomoru* ali nije uspela. (She tried to hide her *jealousy* but failed.)